            <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="https://github.com/OTR500miles2go">Fork on Github</a>
          </div>
          <div class="col l4 offset-l2 s12">
            <h5 class="white-text right-align">Keep In Touch</h5>
            <ul class="contact-list right-align">
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3 right-align" href="https://github.com/OTR500miles2go">GitHub</a></li>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3 right-align" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dianegaydenin/">LinkedIn</a></li>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3 right-align" href="https://twitter.com/GaydenDiane">Twitter</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-copyright">
        <div class="container center-align">
          <a class="grey-text text-lighten-4 center-align" href="https://www.dianegayden.com">Â© 2019 Diane Gayden.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

